text: Ical may refer to: * Calendar (Apple), Apple's personal calendar application, formerly called iCal * ical (Unix), a Tcl/tk calendar package * iCalendar, (The Internet Calendaring and Scheduling Core Object Specification) a standardised calendar data exchange standard * Aburizal Bakrie, a politician. * Muhammad Irsyad Basir, a dangdut singer. * ICaL an ionic current through the L-type calcium channel
title: Ical
